<script>
//IMPORTS
import {computed} from 'vue';
//COMPONENTS
import NavBar from '@/components/NavBar.vue';
export default {
    name : 'InfoProjet',
    components:{
        NavBar,
    },
    props:{
        info_projet : Object,
    },
    setup(props){
        const changeBackground = computed(() =>{
            return {
                backgroundImage: `url(${props.info_projet.image})`
            }
        })


        return {
            changeBackground
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style>
.img{
        width: 17%;
        height: 70%;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position : center;
    }
</style>
